-- Manascale Ley-Seeker is a level 63 elite creature with 118312 hp, 329422 mana, 3022 armor, 50 frost resistance, 50 arcane resistance, and needs to be created. (Is a dragonkin)

-- Surge of Mana - Channeled effect toward a mana user, deals 14000 damage over the course of 8 seconds toward a specific target (Players must focus heals on this target)

-- Draconic Ley Charge - Applied to the boss, has 4 charges, one for each Manascale Ley-Seeker that is alive, Decreases damage taken by 25% per charge.

-- Arcane explosion - Deals 3800 arcane damage within 20 yards

-- Summon Manascale Ley-Seeker - Opens a portal which spawns a Manascale Ley-Seeker (This creature is not like a normal summoned minion and behaves like a spawned creature for the boss fight, is despawned if the fight ends.) (Has a 2 second cast)

-- Summon Manascale Whelps - Spawns 5 Manascale Whelps (This creature is not like a normal summoned minion and behaves like a spawned creature for the boss fight, is despawned if the fight ends.) (has a 2 second cast)

-- Blizzard - Targets a location, and casts blizzard, dealing 12000 damage over the course of 10 seconds in a location, causes a 30% slowing effect for movement speed and casting speed.

-- Gaze of Incantagos - Causes the target to run in fear. ((Casted effect at a random target, gives them terror (Is fear immune, lasts 3 seconds)

-- Guided Ley-Beam - Targets a players location, has a 3.5 second cast time. Deals 15000 arcane damage within a 20 yard radius of the location ((Uses starfall animation?))

-- Arcane Missles - Targets a random player, dealing 14000 arcane damage over 8 seconds

-- Ley-Line Disturbance - Summons a random affinity between Red - Fire, Blue - Frost, Crystal - Physical, Black - Shadow, Green - Nature, and Mana - Arcane

-- Curse of Manascale - Increases the mana cost of all spells by 300%, duration 1hr, curse, cast raid wide every 60-75 seconds
